{"type": "article", "id": 7140, "title": "Lava Plates 盘子", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-06T07:23:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234412oH79Pql6A8nmbt2F.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近用石头做桌面用品的越来越多了，在昨天的“这个设计了不起”里面我们推荐了<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/7093.html\" target=\"_blank\">玄武岩做成的书桌用品</a>，今天我们觉得Peca Studio 和 Ana Saldana 联合推出的这款餐具看起来也不赖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t火山熔岩本身千疮百孔，自带狂野的气质，而抛光的边缘看上去优雅舒畅，两者结合在一起，中和了两种气质。同时，小蜡烛的存在提醒我们餐具的“火烈”的原始面目，简直是自然界原始材料化身当代艺术的优秀作品呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344051wsH2WpKbz3FjMvx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234405XFwtIhUrSBsMWuQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344060AvwDm9cKFR6jhJV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.9804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234406nJY2DyteSRfWIQmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58679707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src